OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774631479
OL,3,CPolitician postpones debate to
OL,4,Clegalise cannabis
OL,6,FThe politician behind the plan to
OL,7,Fconsider the viability of legalising
OL,8,Fcannabis in Guernsey has postponed it
OL,9,Ffollowing allegations against him.
OL,11,FPresident of the Committee for Home
OL,12,FAffairs, Deputy Marc Leadbeater,
OL,13,Flodged a requete to set up a working
OL,14,Fgroup to assess legalising and
OL,15,Fregulating the drug by the end of
OL,16,F2027, but feels the debate, which was
OL,17,Fdue to take place on Wednesday, would
OL,18,Fbe "undermined" and "overshadowed".
OL,26,@uD@Nsr
