PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774631479
OL,3,CPolitician postpones debate to
OL,4,Clegalise cannabis
OL,6,FThe requete is supported by seven
OL,7,Fdeputies, who are concerned by
OL,8,Fwidespread reports of medicinal
OL,9,Fcannabis being resold to those without
OL,10,Fprescriptions.
OL,12,FThey also fear that without further
OL,13,Fregulation, the drug will have
OL,14,Fnegative long-term health consequences
OL,15,Ffor islanders.
OL,26,@nD@Isr
