PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774631479
OL,3,CPolitician postpones debate to
OL,4,Clegalise cannabis
OL,6,FA 2025 report shows that about 11.9%
OL,7,Fof those living in Guernsey and
OL,8,FAlderney over the age of 16 have
OL,9,Freportedly used cannabis across a 12-
OL,10,Fmonth period, while 78.8% of those did
OL,11,Fnot have it prescribed to them.
OL,13,FInterim standards commissioner Andrew
OL,14,FOzanne has commissioned an
OL,15,Finvestigation into Deputy Leadbeater
OL,16,Fover his family connections to
OL,17,Fcompanies likely to benefit from the
OL,18,Flegalisation of cannabis.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
