PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774631479
OL,3,CPolitician postpones debate to
OL,4,Clegalise cannabis
OL,6,FDeputy Leadbeater's sister and parents
OL,7,Fhave shareholdings in House of Green,
OL,8,Fa company that grows medicinal
OL,9,Fcannabis.
OL,11,FHouse of Green is also the parent
OL,12,Fcompany of Bailiwick Botanicals, which
OL,13,Fsells equipment for medicinal cannabis
OL,14,Fuse.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774631479
OL,3,CPolitician postpones debate to
OL,4,Clegalise cannabis
OL,6,FIn an email seen by ITV News, which
OL,7,Fwas sent by Deputy Leadbeater on
OL,8,FMonday, he told States Members: "Over
OL,9,Fthe last few months, there has been a
OL,10,Fsustained and escalating campaign of
OL,11,Funfounded allegations against me, the
OL,12,FCommittee for Home Affairs, and those
OL,13,Fworking under the mandate of the CHA".
OL,15,FHe continued: "There is now a very
OL,16,Freal risk that Wednesday's debate
OL,17,Fwould be overshadowed and undermined,
OL,18,Fand based on what is currently
OL,19,Fcirculating online, that risk has
OL,20,Fbecome a near certainty".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774631479
OL,3,CPolitician postpones debate to
OL,4,Clegalise cannabis
OL,6,FDeputy Leadbeater also said: "My
OL,7,Fintention is to resubmit the requete
OL,8,Fat a later date, once these matters
OL,9,Fhave been properly addressed and my
OL,10,Fname has been cleared."
OL,12,FFurther, in an interview with ITV
OL,13,FNews, Deputy Leadbeater said he had
OL,14,Fnot done anything wrong and called
OL,15,Fclaims that he had not acted in the
OL,16,Fright manner "nonsense".
OL,26,@oD@bsr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774631479
OL,3,CPolitician postpones debate to
OL,4,Clegalise cannabis
OL,6,FHe added: "If these allegations
OL,7,Fagainst me had not been leaked to the
OL,8,Fmedia and not pedalled over social
OL,9,Fmedia, the debate would have gone
OL,10,Fahead, and the accusations could have
OL,11,Fbeen dealt with in the background."
OL,13,FDeputy Curgenven submitted the case
OL,14,Fagainst Deputy Leadbeater, insisting
OL,15,Fthat he had not been honest or
OL,16,Ftransparent over these connections.
OL,18,FDeputy Leadbeater told ITV News he
OL,19,Fbelieves his withdrawal will set back
OL,20,Fwork to legalise cannabis in Guernsey
OL,21,Fby at least a year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
